<h4>24/04/23 0.81</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Minor UI tweaks</li>
<h4>23/04/2023 0.80</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Renamed the app to IndiePass</li>
    <li>Upgraded to Android SDK version 33</li>
    <li>Increased the minimum SDK version to 22</li>
    <li>Various accessibility improvements</li>
    <li>Renamed Night theme to Dark mode</li>
    <li>New dark mode theme</li>
    <li>Improved experience if no account added</li>
    <li>Adjusted app colour palette to improve contrast</li>
    <li>Various minor bug fixes</li>
</ul>
<h4>20/11/2021 0.65</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Set a default account when deleting the current</li>
    <li>Do not set the default microsub endpoint for privacy</li>
    <li>Fix syndication targets switching with multiple accounts</li>
    <li>Temporarily removed push notifications</li>
    <li>Updated app URLs to https://indigenous.marksuth.dev</li>
    <li>Updated app icons</li>
    <li>Updated app accent colour</li>
</ul>
<h4>16/08/2020 0.64</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix IndieWeb global/channel search</li>
    <li>Always show available accounts to set default account</li>
    <li>Allow to set the new connection as the default account</li>
    <li>Fix mp-photo-alt for uploads via IndieWeb media endpoint</li>
</ul>
<h4>02/08/2020 0.63</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix preview of a feed</li>
    <li>Add Pixelfed, Pleroma and Mastodon Account types</li>
    <li>Get more data from server for updating posts</li>
    <li>Pull in more data when sharing to Indigenous</li>
    <li>Fix move post presenting the full channel list</li>
    <li>Trip post can receive a GPX file from a share intent</li>
    <li>Do not auto hide error messages, they must be closed instead</li>
    <li>Select account when auto post is configured and having multiple accounts</li>
    <li>View sources on channel overview in case the server supports the method=tree call</li>
    <li>Quickly switch accounts from navigation bar for reader, or while creating a post</li>
</ul>
<h4>24/04/2020 0.62</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix crash in going back from trip</li>
</ul>
<h4>24/04/2020 0.61</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix crash in compact mode</li>
    <li>Fix uploading to media endpoint in Upload screen</li>
    <li>Only swap author and name for repost and quotation</li>
    <li>Detect YouTube urls when following a YouTube channel</li>
    <li>Better contrast for all action buttons in dark mode</li>
    <li>Do not cache the timeline when viewing only unread items</li>
    <li>Posts overview (?q=source) now better handles content property</li>
    <li>Check references recursively for reposts, configurable via settings</li>
    <li>Introduce trip post type: can read in GPX to post GeoURI's into the route property.</li>
    <li>Hide channels which don't have new items (via menu). Defaults to all and all channels will be visible in case all are read.</li>
</ul>
<h4>29/03/2020 0.60</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Night mode support</li>
    <li>Allow marking items as read while scrolling</li>
    <li>Better indication when the anonymous account is used on startup</li>
</ul>
<h4>25/03/2020 0.59</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Allow setting the post visibility</li>
    <li>Allow setting a default read status</li>
    <li>Add reply option in Posts list (?q=source)</li>
    <li>Allow to open audio in favorite player (e.g. VLC)</li>
    <li>Set syndication target toggled in case "checked" property is available</li>
    <li>Better context of reposts, quotations and likes in timeline. Can be configured in settings.</li>
    <li>Built-in anonymous user with default channels and possibility to post to a custom endpoint with token</li>
</ul>
<h4>15/02/2020 0.58</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Fix search per channel</li>
    <li>Add 'Read' post and response type</li>
    <li>Removed GPS tracker and Mapbox integration</li>
    <li>Allow to show unread items per channel only. Works great if you mark items read manually</li>
    <li>Read and bookmark are optional response types in the Reader. Enable them via settings</li>
</ul>
<h4>08/02/2020 - 0.55 / 0.56 / 0.57</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Use Mapbox to render a location or track points on a map</li>
    <li>Apply filters and add text or emojis to images before posting</li>
    <li>Allow caching channels and timeline posts, configurable via settings</li>
    <li>Cleaner no connection screens and use of snackbar messages where possible</li>
    <li>Updates in settings (e.g. enable contacts/tracker/posts, hide/show post types) have immediate effect in the menu without having to restart the app</li>
</ul>
<h4>06/01/2020 - 0.54</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Allow to attach video or audio to posts. This updates the drafts database, so you will lose any existing drafts.</li>
    <li>Allow to use the media endpoint for media attached to posts. It's a setting you must toggle in the settings screen in the "Media" section.</li>
    <li>Simple GPS tracker to track your itineraries. (Play Store version only at the moment, F-Droid coming later)</li>
    <li>Fix crash with drafts in case the captions were empty and then trying to save the draft again</li>
</ul>
